Package: bashit
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: archerprojects <archer.projects@proton.me>
Description: Bash command file curator and profile manager
 Curate, profile, and manage bash history and command files.
 Lock resident commands, switch profiles, and export clean history.
Depends: libc6, libgcc-s1, libgl1, libxcb1, libxcb-render0, libxcb-shape0, libxcb-xfixes0, libxkbcommon0
